The pure class interface. 
public class Failures
  extends Exception
Failures thrown by the session system. These exceptions represent a normal error condition in operation, and need to be declared in the throws class of method, or to be caught.

Author:
Wolfgang Grieskamp (wg@cs.tu-berlin.de)
